---

<section id="workflows" class="audience" aria-labelledby="workflows-heading">
  <div class="audience__inner">
    <p class="audience__lede">Common workflows</p>
    <h2 id="workflows-heading" class="audience__heading">
      <span class="audience__heading-name">Build and configure.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="audience__grid">
      <a class="audience__card" href="/tutorials/protect-an-api/">
        <p class="audience__card-eyebrow">Gateway</p>
        <h3 class="audience__card-title">Protect an HTTP API</h3>
        <p class="audience__card-body">Route requests through Gateway and require a Caracal mandate before upstream access.</p>
        <span class="audience__card-cta">Protect an API →</span>
      </a>
      <a class="audience__card" href="/guides/resources-providers/">
        <p class="audience__card-eyebrow">Resources</p>
        <h3 class="audience__card-title">Define resources and providers</h3>
        <p class="audience__card-body">Separate protected targets from upstream credential modes.</p>
        <span class="audience__card-cta">Configure resources →</span>
      </a>
      <a class="audience__card" href="/guides/author-policy/">
        <p class="audience__card-eyebrow">Policy</p>
        <h3 class="audience__card-title">Author and activate policy</h3>
        <p class="audience__card-body">Write Rego decisions and activate policy sets safely for a zone.</p>
        <span class="audience__card-cta">Author policy →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
